flowchart TD
    A[PM opens task detail page] --> B[System loads task data and current owner]
    B --> C[PM opens AI agent selector]
    C --> D[System loads valid active AI agents]
    D --> E{Agent selected?}
    E -- No --> F[No change]
    E -- Yes --> G[PM submits assignment]
    G --> H[API authenticates user]
    H --> I{Authorized to manage tasks?}
    I -- No --> J[Return 403 and show error]
    I -- Yes --> K[Validate request payload and agent id]
    K --> L{Valid task and valid active agent?}
    L -- No --> M[Return 400 or 404 and keep owner unchanged]
    L -- Yes --> N[Update task owner in persistence layer]
    N --> O[Write audit log event with old and new owner]
    O --> P[Return updated task payload]
    P --> Q[UI refreshes task detail and task card]
    Q --> R[Assigned agent queue/inbox reflects new ownership]

    N --> S{Concurrent update conflict?}
    S -- Yes --> T[Return 409 and prompt refresh]
    S -- No --> O
